                <componentInstanceProperties>
                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>Hi {{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Welcome to 10X Health!&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
My name is Marco Leal, and I will be your dedicated wellness concierge and my role is to help facilitate your growth and success within the 10X Health System.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Moving forward,&lt;strong&gt; I will be your primary contact &lt;/strong&gt;and liaison between you and the medical team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
I&amp;rsquo;ll check in with you frequently to ensure you are getting the most out of your program and that all of your questions have been addressed and answered.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Next Steps&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;u&gt;Review treatment instructions.&lt;/u&gt; Our medical coordinator will send you an email regarding your medical instructions. If you feel you need further instruction, we can schedule a face-to-face tutorial with a member of our medical team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;u&gt;Follow-up labs&lt;/u&gt;. Your next set of lab work will be due &lt;strong&gt;6-8 weeks&lt;/strong&gt; after starting your program. This step ensures that your hormones are being optimized and you are feeling your best.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Of course, feel free to call me with questions anytime throughout your journey.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Congratulations on taking this big step for you and your health. I look forward to guiding you on your path to a happy, healthier you.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Yours in good health,&lt;br /&gt;
